@startuml Admin_UserManagement

title Admin - User Management

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"

rectangle "USER MANAGEMENT" {
    usecase "List All Candidates" as AM1
    usecase "List All Recruiters" as AM2
    usecase "View User Details" as AM3
    usecase "Lock User Account" as AM4
    usecase "Unlock User Account" as AM5
    usecase "Search User\nBy Email/Name" as AM6
}

Admin --> AM1: 1. List candidates
AM1 --> AM3: View details
AM1 --> AM6: Search user
AM3 --> AM4: 2. Lock account
AM3 --> AM5: 3. Unlock account

Admin --> AM2: 4. List recruiters
AM2 --> AM3: View details
AM2 --> AM6: Search user
AM3 --> AM4: Lock account
AM3 --> AM5: Unlock account

note right of AM1
  **Priority:** P1 (Important)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
